text: Ingstad may refer to: * 8993 Ingstad, a main-belt asteroid, named after Helge Ingstad * Ingstad Family Media, a broadcasting company in North Dakota, United States == People == * Helge Ingstad (1899–2001), a Norwegian explorer. * Marcus Pløen Ingstad (1837–1918), a Norwegian professor of law and legal scholar * Anne Stine Ingstad (1918–1997), a Norwegian archaeologist and wife of Helge Ingstad * Vilde Ingstad (born 1994), a Norwegian handball player
